videos.headline: Dinich: 'I think Alabama is done'
videos.description: Heather Dinich gives her long-term prognosis for Alabama after its loss to LSU, with the Crimson Tide not having the opportunity to bounce back.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Analysis (Dinich: ‘I think Alabama is done’ ) 2019/11/9 College Football Show
